  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I figured out why it was happening. I am using the angular material Expansion Panel for my hits. I'm guessing that the expansion panel is quite expensive to render so as you're typing away in the instant search text box, the page locks up since it's trying to repaint the dom.\r\n\r\nI commented out my expansion panel for the hits and just changed it to a simple div. The page no longer locks up and everything works as expected.",
